{"tid":477183,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[有圖]有無人12月18-26去越南芽莊","createTime":"2017-11-22T18:46:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-23T16:34:40.000Z","uid":89610,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"eef676b38d59b45afc7eb8c11ca26e847ea78ef4","tid":477183,"uid":89610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T18:46:55.000Z","msg":"見到呢個時間來回機票連稅$1000唔洗, 但同friend夾唔岩時間我又要清假, 之前一條友去美國加拿大exchange都好玩, 不過多伴可以share(交通住宿食野等等), 自己一個難試得多野食, 睇下有無人有興趣去3-4日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n芽莊12月大概24-28度唔會熱到hihi又唔會凍<br />\n除左出名既婆那加占婆塔,芽莊大教堂,珍珠島之外<br />\n都想試下local tour 四島游，潛水tour, 泥漿浴等等<br />\n<br />\ngoogle搵既示意圖:<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/23/020406_fb7459b14830e60a977006846dced47c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F23%2F020406_fb7459b14830e60a977006846dced47c.jpg&h=d0ec7d50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n婆那加占婆塔<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/23/020538_a5d7bb9a85e760cdda8a997cccc64e82.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F23%2F020538_a5d7bb9a85e760cdda8a997cccc64e82.jpg&h=a466ed13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n芽莊大教堂<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/23/020716_dd75fe975c49625a1c2bccc00d98e5ca.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F23%2F020716_dd75fe975c49625a1c2bccc00d98e5ca.jpeg&h=b8acb44d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/23/020721_242fab3ef33fe194ac42996f08b3c7e3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F23%2F020721_242fab3ef33fe194ac42996f08b3c7e3.png&h=3c5160de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/23/020725_37505ab0eecf46a192c0161cae9f7e20.jpg\" 